children.name: Follow these steps to create your application:
children.characters: Follow these steps to create your application:

children.name: Send us your Application Name, preferred BundleID, and Application Type (tethered or mobile) via the Create New Application button, or via email to xxxxxx@core.com. We will respond to confirm your details and provide you with a secure Core Key. Once confirmed, input your Core Key and Bundle ID into Unity (do not share your Core Key with anyone). Unity will verify your details and you will be ready to begin development. If you have any questions, contact us using our Support Page.
